  "detailed_description": "<h1>ADD TO WISHLIST</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857730/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.poster.avif?t=1682476394\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857730/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.webm?t=1682476394\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857730/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.mp4?t=1682476394\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><strong> Color Patterns </strong> is a minimalist puzzle game inspired by the classic board game domino.<br><br>- Designed for <strong>puzzle lovers</strong>;<br>- Solve 40 carefully crafted challenging levels;<br>- Minimalist design. No score, timer or pressure;<br>- Mouse-only controls. Left click to move pieces between spaces. Right click on the pieces to rotate;<br><br>Follow the symbols of each color to solve the puzzle.<br>Red: <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857730/extras/db3ef0ccf82a80ac0514c2577e8026b4.webp?t=1682476394\" width=15 height=15 /></span>     Green: <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857730/extras/488336b7d5c4b9cdd56bc4472ae79de6.webp?t=1682476394\" width=15 height=15 /></span>     Blue: <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857730/extras/cbc9d52746128ee04a350ff2dda53093.webp?t=1682476394\" width=15 height=15 /></span>     Yellow: <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857730/extras/25aca2871a53ba9c8c1464131f3d556d.webp?t=1682476394\" width=15 height=15 /></span><br><br>A challenging puzzle game that requires attention. With carefully crafted levels, the challenge is to find the correct patterns on the board. Some pieces <strong>can</strong> work in more than one position.<br><br>Can you find the correct pattern that will solve each puzzle? <strong> Try it out </strong> and show that you are a puzzle expert.",
  "about_the_game": "<strong> Color Patterns </strong> is a minimalist puzzle game inspired by the classic board game domino.<br><br>- Designed for <strong>puzzle lovers</strong>;<br>- Solve 40 carefully crafted challenging levels;<br>- Minimalist design. No score, timer or pressure;<br>- Mouse-only controls. Left click to move pieces between spaces. Right click on the pieces to rotate;<br><br>Follow the symbols of each color to solve the puzzle.<br>Red: <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857730/extras/db3ef0ccf82a80ac0514c2577e8026b4.webp?t=1682476394\" width=15 height=15 /></span>     Green: <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857730/extras/488336b7d5c4b9cdd56bc4472ae79de6.webp?t=1682476394\" width=15 height=15 /></span>     Blue: <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857730/extras/cbc9d52746128ee04a350ff2dda53093.webp?t=1682476394\" width=15 height=15 /></span>     Yellow: <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857730/extras/25aca2871a53ba9c8c1464131f3d556d.webp?t=1682476394\" width=15 height=15 /></span><br><br>A challenging puzzle game that requires attention. With carefully crafted levels, the challenge is to find the correct patterns on the board. Some pieces <strong>can</strong> work in more than one position.<br><br>Can you find the correct pattern that will solve each puzzle? <strong> Try it out </strong> and show that you are a puzzle expert.",
